OL,3,CTransport Secretary to draw 'line in
OL,4,Cthe sand' over HS2 as she reveals
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FThe Transport Secretary is set to lift
OL,8,Fthe lid on the lack of oversight that
OL,9,Fcontributed to the spiralling costs of
OL,10,FHS2.
OL,12,FHeidi Alexander will tell the Commons
OL,13,Fon Wednesday that she is drawing a
OL,14,F"line in the sand" over the
OL,15,Fbeleaguered rail project, as the
OL,16,FGovernment attempts to reset how major
OL,17,Finfrastructure is delivered.
