OL,3,CTransport Secretary to draw 'line in
OL,4,Cthe sand' over HS2 as she reveals
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FMinisters plan to learn from the
OL,8,Fmistakes of HS2 so that they do a
OL,9,Fbetter job when it comes to projects
OL,10,Flike Northern Powerhouse Rail and the
OL,11,FLower Thames Crossing, it is
OL,12,Funderstood.
OL,14,F"HS2 has made Britain a laughing stock
OL,15,Fin terms of its ability to deliver big
OL,16,Finfrastructure projects, and it has to
OL,17,Fend. This will set out the way we will
OL,18,Fdo that," a Government source told the
OL,19,FPA news agency.
