OL,7,FThe result of two reviews into HS2 are
OL,8,Fexpected to be announced alongside the
OL,9,FTransport Secretary's statement.
OL,11,FThe first of these is an interim
OL,12,Freport by Mark Wild, the chief
OL,13,Fexecutive of HS2, who was appointed
OL,14,Flate last year.
OL,16,FHe will assess the construction of the
OL,17,Fproject's first phase from London to
OL,18,FBirmingham.
