OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FA second, wider review into the
OL,8,Fgovernance and accountability of HS2,
OL,9,Fled by James Stewart, will also report
OL,10,Fback.
OL,12,FThis is expected to set out what has
OL,13,Fgone wrong with the project, and what
OL,14,Fministers can learn for future
OL,15,Finfrastructure projects.
OL,17,FAs she addresses MPs, the Transport
OL,18,FSecretary is expected to address
OL,19,Fallegations of fraud by contractors to
OL,20,FHS2 which have emerged recently.
