OL,7,FEarlier this week, it emerged HS2 Ltd
OL,8,Freported a sub-contractor working on
OL,9,Fthe rail line to HMRC following an
OL,10,Finternal probe.
OL,12,FDuring the statement, Ms Alexander is
OL,13,Falso set to announce a new chair of
OL,14,FHS2.
OL,16,FThe current chair, Sir Jon Thompson,
OL,17,Fpreviously announced he would stand
OL,18,Fdown in the spring of this year.
