OL,7,FHis replacement will be Mike Brown,
OL,8,Faccording to The Daily Telegraph
OL,9,Fnewspaper.
OL,11,FMr Brown is the former commissioner
OL,12,Ffor Transport for London, who helped
OL,13,Fto oversee the deliver of Crossrail,
OL,14,Fthe transport project which became
OL,15,FLondon's Elizabeth Line.
