OL,3,CTransport Secretary to draw 'line in
OL,4,Cthe sand' over HS2 as she reveals
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FHS2 was originally due to run between
OL,8,FLondon and Birmingham, then onto
OL,9,FManchester and Leeds, but the project
OL,10,Fwas severely curtailed by the
OL,11,FConservatives in power due to
OL,12,Fspiralling costs.
OL,14,FConcerns about the costs of the
OL,15,Fstunted project have persisted, with
OL,16,F#100 million spent on a bat tunnel
OL,17,Faimed at mitigating the railway's
OL,18,Fenvironmental impact singled out by
OL,19,FSir Keir Starmer for criticism.
